# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Cortex environment variables
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Speechmatics API key — used ONLY by the serverless function
# (api/speechmatics-token.js) to mint short-lived browser tokens.
# Never exposed to the client. Set this in Vercel → Project → Settings →
# Environment Variables, and in a local .env.local for `vercel dev`.
SPEECHMATICS_API_KEY=your-speechmatics-api-key-here

# Google Gemini key is entered by the user inside the app (Settings) and
# stored locally in their browser — it is NOT configured here.
